## âš¡ Quick Start (5 Minutes)

### 1. Copy Files to Your Project
```bash
# Copy the 3 React components
cp CreateInvoice.js src/components/admin/invoices/
cp InvoiceDetails.js src/components/admin/invoices/
cp InvoiceList.js src/components/admin/invoices/
```

### 2. Add Your Logo
```bash
# Create assets folder and copy logo
mkdir -p src/assets
cp logo.jpg src/assets/
```

### 3. Install Dependencies (if needed)
```bash
npm install react-router-dom lucide-react
```

### 4. Verify Logo Path
Each file imports the logo. Verify this path matches your structure:
```javascript
import logo from "../../../assets/logo.jpg";
```

Adjust `../../../` if your folder structure is different.

### 5. Done! ğŸ‰
Your invoice system is ready to use.

