## ğŸ”§ Technical Details

### Color Scheme
```
Primary Blue:   #003B6A (headers, buttons)
Secondary Blue: #004B7A (gradients)
Accent Orange:  #FF8C42 (action buttons)
Success Green:  #22C55E (status indicators)
```

### Dependencies
```json
{
  "react": "18+",
  "react-router-dom": "6+",
  "lucide-react": "0.263.1+"
}
```

### Data Storage
- **Method**: Browser LocalStorage
- **Format**: JSON array of invoice objects
- **Persistence**: Until browser cache is cleared
- **Best For**: Small to medium invoices

### Invoice Data Structure
```javascript
{
  id: "INV-123456",           // Auto-generated
  customer: {
    name: "John Doe",
    phone: "+91 98765 43210",
    address: "123 Main St",
    bikeModel: "Pulsar 150",
    bikeNumber: "WB-02-AB-1234",
    invoiceDate: "2024-01-15",
    dueDate: "2024-02-15"
  },
  items: [
    {
      id: 1,
      description: "Oil Change",
      quantity: 1,
      price: 500
    }
  ],
  grandTotal: 900,
  status: "Unpaid",
  createdAt: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
}
```

