## ğŸ–¨ï¸ Printing & PDF

### Print Invoice
1. Navigate to invoice details
2. Click "Print Invoice" button
3. Choose printer
4. Click Print

Print preview will show:
- âœ… Logo in white container
- âœ… All colors and styling
- âœ… Professional layout
- âœ… Perfect formatting

### Generate PDF (Optional)
To enable PDF download, install html2pdf:

```bash
npm install html2pdf.js
```

Then update the `handleDownloadPDF` function in InvoiceDetails.js:

```javascript
const handleDownloadPDF = () => {
  const element = componentRef.current;
  const opt = {
    margin: 10,
    filename: `invoice-${invoice.id}.pdf`,
    image: { type: 'jpeg', quality: 0.98 },
    html2canvas: { scale: 2 },
    jsPDF: { orientation: 'portrait', unit: 'mm', format: 'a4' }
  };
  html2pdf().set(opt).from(element).save();
};
```

