## ğŸ¯ Usage Examples

### Create an Invoice
1. Click "Generate New Bill" button on invoice list
2. Fill in customer information
3. Enter vehicle details
4. Add service items (click "Add Item" to add more)
5. Enter description, quantity, and price for each item
6. Click "Save & Generate Bill"

### View an Invoice
1. Go to "Invoice Records" page
2. Click the eye icon next to any invoice
3. View the formatted invoice
4. Click "Print Invoice" to print
5. Click "Download PDF" to save as PDF

### Search & Filter
1. On the invoice list page
2. Type in search box to find by name, ID, or vehicle
3. Click status buttons to filter (All, Paid, Unpaid)
4. Results update in real-time

### Delete an Invoice
1. On invoice list, find the invoice
2. Click the trash icon
3. Confirm deletion
4. Invoice is removed permanently

